able decisions.\n\nMore than a data system, the Data Engine is where information becomes intelligence, foresight, and strategic advantage.\n<BR><BR>\nAcross the agricultural sector, data is often:\n\nfragmented across multiple sources and systems, difficult to access or interpret, not actionable for farmers or decision-makers, underutilized in real-time operations. Without reliable data, decisions are based on guesswork rather than insight.\n\nThe Data Engine was developed to change this.\n\nIt is built on a simple principle:\n\nBetter data leads to better decisions\u2014and better outcomes.\n\nThe Data Engine creates a central intelligence layer that powers every part of the IFU ecosystem.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__text-box -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner__content -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__button wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\"   class=\"cherito-btn\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__text\">Data Engine Login<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--1\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--2\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--3\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--4\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--5\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a><!-- \/.cherito-btn -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__button -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__content -->\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.col-lg-6 -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight\" data-wow-duration=\"1800ms\">